3D chess program in OpenGl and C
[![perl dark](https://github.com/altercation/solarized/raw/master/img/screen-perl-dark-th.png)](https://github.com/altercation/solarized/raw/master/img/screen-perl-dark.png)

[![Screenshot of the current state of the project](https://github.com/darksmo/gl-smochess/blob/master/gl-smochess.png)](Screenshot)

- compile: make
- run: ./chessboard

Move around the chessboard using the keys:

              .---- forward
camera down - q w e --- camera up
     left --- a s d --- right
                '
                `---- backward

Highlight cells:
             .---- forward
            t 
 left --- f g h --- right
            '
             `---- backward

Select pawn: p

Tested on MacOSX 10.6.8
